formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1. FSI cost borne by Land owners and hence not reflected in Land Cost.

2. Total Cost of Cost of Project has exceeded the Estimated Cost as per records provided to us.

3. Collection is deposited in Naroda Nagrik Co-operative Bank.  As, not all collection is deposited in RERA designated Bank Account, total deposits and collection made in Naroda Nagrik Bank Account are considered as withdrawal for point 7 and 8 of the certificate.

4. As explained to us, there are no Documented Loan Agreements entered into as loans received were unsecured.

5. Further it has been verbally explained to us that no units have been given as mortgage to any lender by promoter.
6. This certificate is being issued based on the records and documents produced by management and verification of books of accounts till 18/11/2019. However, after the additional information section of the certificate  due to system error the date column is non editable and it shows wrong date i.e., 07/11/2019.
